{"tid":2074640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨[s]港[/s]鐵下月起推八達通八折車費優惠　為期半年","createTime":"2020-06-22T09:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T13:41:00.000Z","uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4cf7928a7bba00e190c3a221120ed486925f35ab","tid":2074640,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:01:43.000Z","msg":"2020-06-22 HKT 16:54<br />\n <br />\n黨<del>港</del>鐵宣布為期半年的新一輪疫情支援措施，下月1日起將現時八達通「程程3.3%車費扣減」，大幅提升至「程程20%車費扣減」，並為常客車票計劃提供100元扣減，優惠直至明年1月1日。<br />\n<br />\n黨<del>港</del>鐵說，新優惠連同現行的「早晨折扣優惠」，成人八達通乘客可享高達約四五折優惠。如果購買今年7月至12月的「全月通加強版」及「黨<del>港</del>鐵都會票」，則可扣減100元，乘客可於星期三起以優惠價購買下月的「全月通加強版」。"},{"pid":"ea168de9e7e4cf2c896d6e1738aea371f612f83a","tid":2074640,"uid":54800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:02:14.000Z","msg":"睇黎黨<del>港</del>鐵真係蝕得好甘........."},{"pid":"1e08264315eac264f0e6a8a4e3aaa5b1cc87ad5d","tid":2074640,"uid":34553,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:02:53.000Z","msg":"免費我就搭"},{"pid":"34febb452cbdfdbd52e3c37e11634878fa865e74","tid":2074640,"uid":95138,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:03:19.000Z","msg":"用綠卡係咪俾$1.6<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a715db5281c1cdab21e9fdb47016d37fc08d6b","tid":2074640,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"賣下樓咪有錢<br />\n黨鐵副業黎姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9d8f94f51cfd60a935c5422b7146cbf8818d08","tid":2074640,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea168de9e7e4cf2c896d6e1738aea371f612f83a","tid":2074640,"uid":54800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:02:14.000Z","msg":"睇黎黨<del>港</del>鐵真係蝕得好甘........."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" c